{"tid":850902,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【10月新番】學園BASARA 集中討論區","createTime":"2018-10-06T18:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T09:26:31.000Z","uid":206080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0305ffc9de641aede8149b83a63734c992d5e54a","tid":850902,"uid":206080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T18:17:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/020321_cb003f39561f65a56b6a835d904e0dfe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F020321_cb003f39561f65a56b6a835d904e0dfe.png&h=75518489&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>劇情簡介</strong><br />\nBASARA學園今天也在展開棒球部王牌伊達政宗<br />\n和足球部王牌真田幸村的熱血戰鬥。<br />\n再加上前任學生會長豐臣秀吉遭到停學處分，<br />\n圍繞着下任會長的寶座，學園陷入群雄割據的亂世而騷動不安。<br />\n呼喊着羈絆之力的德川家康與為了打倒家康而燃燒熱情的石田三成<br />\n也開始了天下分水嶺之戰。<br />\n另一方面，戀愛的糾紛也在愚蠢的活動當中連日爆發！<br />\n這所過於混沌的BASARA學園究竟會不會有明天？！<br />\n<br />\n2018年10月4日開始在TBS電視台播出。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>STAFF</strong><br />\n原作：CAPCOM（《學園BASARA》）<br />\n原作監修：小林裕幸（CAPCOM）、山本真（CAPCOM）<br />\n監督：大原實<br />\n系列構成：三浦浩兒<br />\n角色設計：高田晴仁<br />\n總作畫監督：相坂直紀<br />\n美術監督：荒井和浩<br />\n道具設計：小川浩<br />\n色彩設計：福田由布子<br />\n攝影監督：織田賴信<br />\n編輯：池田康隆<br />\n音響監督：岩浪美和<br />\n音響製作：DAX Production<br />\n音樂：立山秋航（HIGH KICK ENTERTAINMENT）<br />\nBGM製作：HIGH KICK ENTERTAINMENT<br />\n動畫製作協力：MARU畫 FACTORY<br />\n動畫製作：Brain's Base<br />\n<br />\n<strong>CAST</strong><br />\n伊達政宗：中井和哉<br />\n真田幸村：保志總一朗<br />\n片倉小十郎：森川智之<br />\n猿飛佐助：子安武人<br />\n德川家康：增田俊樹<br />\n石田三成：關智一<br />\n前田慶次：森田成一<br />\n長曾我部元親：石野龍三<br />\n毛利元就：中原茂<br />\n春日：桑谷夏子<br />\n阿市：能登麻美子<br />\n鶴姬：小清水亞美<br />\n阿松：甲斐田裕子<br />\n大谷吉繼：立木文彥<br />\n前田利家：坪井智浩<br />\n小早川秀秋：福山潤<br />\n淺井長政：辻谷耕史<br />\n伊月：澤城美雪<br />\n島左近：中村悠一<br />\n柴田勝家：岡本信彥<br />\n後藤又兵衛：三木真一郎<br />\n黑田官兵衛：小山力也<br />\n竹中半兵衛：石田彰<br />\n豐臣秀吉：置鯰龍太郎<br />\n雜賀孫市：大原沙耶香<br />\n上杉謙信：朴璐美<br />\n武田信玄：玄田哲章<br />\n明智光秀：速水獎<br />\n織田信長：若本規夫<br />\n<br />\n<strong>片頭曲</strong><br />\n〈誇れ 気高き 美しき、いきざまを〉<br />\n歌：EIGHT OF TRIANGLE<br />\n作詞：君島零，作曲：遠藤和斗、深澤祐貴，編曲：遠藤和斗、久下真音<br />\n<br />\n<strong>主題歌</strong><br />\n〈Be Affected〉<br />\n歌：西川貴教 &times; Fear, and Loathing in Las Vegas<br />\n作詞、作曲、編曲：Fear, and Loathing in Las Vegas<br />\n<br />\nPV<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PtDB2_SKajg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPtDB2_SKajg&d=zRNiB%2B%2BwfEuD5CG11Lg190bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=4f57dbaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PtDB2_SKajg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tbs.co.jp/anime/gakuen_basara\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tbs.co.jp%2Fanime%2Fgakuen_basara&d=zRNiB%2B%2BwfEuD5CG11Lg190bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=ce591d0e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tbs.co.jp/anime/gakuen_basara</a></div>"},{"pid":"8bd9bd895207799b962bfffe93a96b85f183815d","tid":850902,"uid":206080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T18:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e8c92bfb3f341975f6876904e5d90239735850","tid":850902,"uid":206080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:36:26.000Z","msg":"慘 冇人睇"},{"pid":"337b8c3c31bd2b757e3c0ab283706dcab4715265","tid":850902,"uid":206080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa59159adad19ae9481ac579828179ebebba7d0","tid":850902,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T19:52:34.000Z","msg":"你話做返戰國嗰時就話好睇<br />\n你老味學園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248168b23b9975a5636e14fda30933d5f9610769","tid":850902,"uid":206080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:54:17.000Z","msg":"但BASARA4個劇本好弱 唔夠連貫<br />\n<br />\n好難動畫化"},{"pid":"99803a2448eb3ce826e5e867829faccdc3553f23","tid":850902,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite